\title{Constrained Sectorial Search Command}
\description{
An \link[R6:R6Class]{R6} class that configures a constrained sectorial search
in \pkg{nitro}.

Constrained sectorial searches select sectors of the tree based on
constraint groups defined by fork (node) ranges, and then perform branch
swapping within each sector. This wraps the \code{sectsch} TNT command with
the \code{css} subcommand.
}
